# ==== Commit Messages =============================================================

# ==== Commit Title (Commit Summary) Format ========================================
# <emoji> <type>: #<Issue Number> <subject>
#
# <description>
#
# ==== Example =====================================================================
# âœ¨ feat: Create shared display components for top and service pages
# âœï¸ fix: #123 Corrected a typo in the Terms of Use

# ==== Type ( Prefix ) =============================================================
# fix: ------------------ Bug fix
# hotfix: --------------- Emergency bug fix
# feat: ----------------- New feature (short for feature)
# docs: ----------------- Documentation-only changes
# style: ---------------- Code formatting changes like whitespace, line breaks, etc.
# refactor:	------------- Code restructuring
# test: ----------------- Adding or correcting tests
# chore: ---------------- Changes related to build tools or auto-generated files/libraries

# ==== Emojis ======================================================================
# ğŸ› :bug: --------------- Bug fix (fix)
# ğŸ©¹ :adhesive_bandage: -- Fix Lint errors or code style (style)
# ğŸš§ :construction: ------ WIP - Work In Progress (style)
# âœ¨ :sparkles: ---------- New feature (feat)
# ğŸ‰ :tada: -------------- Major feature release worth celebrating (feat)
# ğŸš€ :rocket: ------------ Performance improvements (feat)
# ğŸ¨ :art: --------------- Visual changes like CSS styling (feat)
# ğŸ’„ :lipstick: ---------- UI improvements(feat)
# ğŸ”’ï¸ :lock: -------------- Security improvements  (feat)
# âœï¸ :pencil: ------------ Fix typos (docs)
# ğŸ“ :memo: -------------- Documentation updates  (docs)
# â™»ï¸ :recycle: ----------- Code refactoring (refactor)
# ğŸ”¥ :shower: ------------ Remove code or files. (refactor)
# ğŸ’š :green_heart: ------- Fix CI builds or test improvements  (test)
# â¬†ï¸ :arrow_up: ---------- Dependency updates (chore)
